<!-- Product -->
<section class="section-product py-20">
    <div class="container wrapper">
        <h2 class="heading-tertiary">Risk Analysis, Audit & Review</h2>
        <p class="mb-16 leading-loose">We offer risk inspection, gap analysis and policy document review services for suggesting improvements if any in your insurance plans, in consideration of your business profile, operationsal aspects and claim history. We undertake such services at a fast pace and our "Risk Review Report" provides a very handy tool for the Management to understand and emphasize on the importance of proper risk management practices.</p>

        <h3 class="heading-tertiary mb-4">Understanding your Business and Risk Analysis</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-8">
            <li class="mb-4">Site (office/factory/warehouse/highway) visit</li>
            <li class="mb-4">Identifyication & analysis of all risks that may pose on your business.</li>
            <li class="mb-4">Scrutinize & analyze existing insurance Coverage in detail and suggesting possible improvement, avoiding overlapping of coverages</li>
            <li class="mb-4">Arranging need based risk inspection and valuation</li>
            <li class="mb-4">Mapping your existing coverage on the risks that need to be covered.</li>
            <li class="mb-4">Identification of any uncovered risk and gap in the insurance cover</li>
            <li class="mb-4">Submitting a Risk Review Report.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

</MainLayout>


<style lang="scss">
    .product-hero {
        width: 100%;
        background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff, #32A2D1);
    }
</style>